        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You have trained in the use of weapons both above and below water. You have familiarity with @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Crossbow]{crossbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Heavy Crossbow]{heavy crossbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Dagger]{daggers}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Longspear]{longspears}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Spear]{spears}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Trident]{tridents}—for the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons. You don't take a –2 circumstance penalty to melee slashing or bludgeoning attacks while underwater.</p>"
        },
